    public abstract class AbstractPNGraphics<P extends AbstractPlace<F,S>,T extends AbstractTransition<F,S>,F extends AbstractFlowRelation<P,T,S>,M extends AbstractMarking<S>,S>
extends java.lang.Object

    Abstract petri net graphics super class. It contains all net type specific graphical information needed to draw the petri net.

    Adrian Lange
